es into Solutions</h2>\n            <p>We harness cutting-edge biotechnology to address complex challenges in health, agriculture, and environmental science.</p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Our Core Strengths</h2>\n            <div class=\"features\">\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-microscope\"></i>\n                    <h3>Research & Development</h3>\n                    <p>Pushing the boundaries of scientific knowledge with state-of-the-art research facilities.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-dna\"></i>\n                    <h3>Genetic Engineering</h3>\n                    <p>Developing innovative genetic solutions for improved crop yields and disease resistance.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-pills\"></i>\n                    <h3>Therapeutic Innovation</h3>\n                    <p>Creating novel therapies to combat unmet medical needs and improve patient outcomes.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                    <i class=\"fas fa-seedling\"></i>\n                    <h3>Sustainable Solutions</h3>\n                    <p>Leveraging biotechnology for eco-friendly agricultural practices and environmental restoration.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"cta-section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Join Us in Shaping a Better Tomorrow</h2>\n            <a href=\"#contact\" class=\"cta-button\">Contact Us</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Innovate BioTech. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Basic JavaScript for potential future enhancements or interactive elements\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            console.log(\"Innovate BioTech website loaded!\");\n            // Add smooth scrolling for anchor links if needed\n            document.querySelectorAll('a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n                anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                    e.preventDefault();\n                    document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                        behavior: 'smooth'\n                    });\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}